  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    GFSL launches apprenticeship scheme
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Gov Facility Services Ltd (GFSL) is proud to announce the launch of our new apprenticeship programme, helping people to develop their skills and careers.</p>

  </div>
</div>

